    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras/a3dfeb7d6b6c7ed8b303f7e170edf0ed.avif?t=1758901833\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras_big/a3dfeb7d6b6c7ed8b303f7e170edf0ed.webp?t=1758901833 width=1560 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>S.M.A.C.K.</strong> is an online multiplayer, third-person, sandbox shooter, where you suck up objects around the map and fire them at your friends with a specialized set of weapons placed within the arena. ANYTHING IS AMMO! Utilize the props and weapons on the map and fire away! Your friends won't be talkin' S.M.A.C.K. anymore after receiving a forklift to the face!  Want to use only snipers? With Explosions? And Moon Gravity?  Customize your bot and play your own way with configurable game modes and sandbox options. Take a trip down memory lane with classic game-play feel and some added twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras/158d5cf4a1406791283f7ba4cf826451.poster.avif?t=1758901833\" width=780 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras/158d5cf4a1406791283f7ba4cf826451.webm?t=1758901833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras/158d5cf4a1406791283f7ba4cf826451.mp4?t=1758901833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>!Note for playtest!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >S.M.A.C.K. is still under active development and being updated on a live test branch, you will see updates often and I could push an update that breaks the entire game at any time, please be patient and report any bugs or feedback on the Discord channel</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>discord(dot)gg/EJ8C77XS3H</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras/8f28333bbc3d96d45772a0600302f803.webp?t=1758901833\" width=155 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118060/extras/6da9266626188c4c7c0ec2ac8f388073.avif?t=1758901833\" width=480 height=156 /></span></p>",
